	$LF
	"This movie improves Chatterbox's TAS by 2 frames (Making The Time 4:54.70) by having a faster 2nd room (Walljump room) and 4th room (Water room) of 8-4. I will explain how we improved it in a bit, but for now let's discuss the movie level by level.
	$LF
